file=Product/spec/logical/book-requirements.md · h=name: spec-logical-book-requirements\ntype: logical\nstatus: built — inherits from Shared OS (2026-07-15)\nassigned_agent: spec (Product / Product Manager — department leader)\ndate_added: 2026-07-10\ndate_filled: 2026-07-15\n · p:=All logical scripts live in `Shared OS/logical/` (playbook §13.5). Spec inherits scripts from the shared layer — no dedicated scripts needed. This file is the only file in this folder.\n · tb=\| Script \| Source Book \| Book URL \| Why Spec Needs It \| · tb=\|--------\|------------\|----------\|---------------------\| · tb=\| `rice_prioritization.py` \| Intercom RICE + Reinersten WSJF + SAFe \| Canonical standard (Tier B) \| RICE weights, cost-of-delay, effort calibration for backlog ranking \| · tb=\| `decision_analysis.py` \| Clemen & Reilly, *Making Hard Decisions* (3rd Ed., 2012) \| [archive.org](https://archive.org/details/makingharddecisi0000clem_u9f9) \| Decision trees, MAUT, EVPI for opportunity assessment and kill/park decisions \| · tb=\| `signal_detection.py` \| OpenStax, *Introductory Business Statistics 2e* (2023) \| [openstax.org](https://openstax.org/details/books/introductory-business-statistics-2e) — FREE \| Evidence-cap coupling: CI checks, significance tests for PRD claims \| · tb=\| `planning_fallacy.py` \| Kahneman, *Thinking, Fast and Slow* (2011) \| [archive.org](https://dn790002.ca.archive.org/0/items/DanielKahnemanThinkingFastAndSlow/) \| De-bias roadmap projections in PRDs \| · tb=\| `experiment_methods.py` \| Kohavi et al., *Trustworthy Online Controlled Experiments* papers + OpenStax \| [experimentguide.com](https://experimentguide.com/) / [openstax.org](https://openstax.org/) \| Power analysis, sample sizing for A/B tests — validates metrics claims \| · tb=\| `pricing_methods.py` \| Nagle, *Strategy and Tactics of Pricing* (2002) + Van Westendorp (1976) \| [archive.org](https://archive.org/details/strategytacticso0000nagl) — FREE \| Revenue guardrail thresholds for PRD financial sections \| · tb=\| Previously Flagged (0.6) \| Status \| Script \| · tb=\|--------------------------\|--------\|--------\| · tb=\| RICE weights + confidence caps \| ✅ Cleared \| `rice_prioritization.py` (RICE scoring + calibrate_effort) \| · tb=\| Cost-of-delay vs RICE's rubric \| ✅ Cleared \| `rice_prioritization.py` (cod_from_rice_factors, WSJF) \| · tb=\| Age-out from actual decay data \| ✅ Cleared \| `signal_detection.py` (detect_metric_drift, classify_metric_change) \| · tb=\| Evidence-cap coupling for PRD claims \| ✅ Cleared \| `signal_detection.py` (CI + significance) + `experiment_methods.py` (power analysis) \| · sm:=- **backlog-rules** → imports `rice_prioritization.py` (RICE, effort calibration)\n- **opportunity-assessment** → imports `decision_analysis.py` (EVPI, decision trees)\n- **prd-discipline** → imports `signal_detection.py` (evidence verification) + `planning_fallacy.py` (projection de-biasing)\n- **acceptance-criteria-handoff** → imports `experiment_methods.py` (MDE, power for acceptance criteria)\n